---
const services = ['样机现场演示', '产线方案评估', '硬件参数详解', '渠道代理洽谈'];
---

<section id="visit" class="relative">
  <div class="hazard"></div>
  <div class="blueprint relative">
    <div
      class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-[var(--gutter)] py-24 text-center md:py-36"
    >
      <p class="tag tag--acc reveal">05 — VISIT · 线下展厅</p>
      <h2
        class="reveal mx-auto mt-6 max-w-3xl text-4xl font-bold leading-snug md:text-5xl"
        style="transition-delay: 80ms"
      >
        来现场，<br class="md:hidden" />看机器如何<span class="text-acc">成长</span>。
      </h2>
      <p
        class="reveal mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-mut"
        style="transition-delay: 160ms"
      >
        参数表说明不了柔性夹爪的手感，视频也拍不出集群调度的默契。预约一次现场演示，把方案聊透。
      </p>

      <div
        class="reveal mx-auto mt-8 flex max-w-2xl flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-2"
        style="transition-delay: 220ms"
      >
        {
          services.map((s) => (
            <span class="tag flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-acc">✓</span>
              {s}
            </span>
          ))
        }
      </div>

      <div
        class="reveal mt-12 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4"
        style="transition-delay: 300ms"
      >
        <a href="mailto:info@airdb.com?subject=预约线下展厅" class="btn btn--solid">
          info@airdb.com <span class="arr">→</span>
        </a>
        <span class="tag">回复通常在 1 个工作日内</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hazard"></div>
</section>
